Class InspectionRoot<T>

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.craft.debug.inspect.InspectionNode<T>

All Implemented Interfaces:
Disposable
@ThreadSafe public final class InspectionRoot<T> extends InspectionNode<T> implements Disposable
The root node of the inspection tree. Inspection trees are a way of determining values within the game. It also allows for inspecting game packets.
Since:
0.1.0
